        public T customRetryForStatusCodes(java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Boolean> customRetryForStatusCodes)
        Deprecated. 
        Set custom retry rules for HTTP status codes received in emit responses from the Collector. By default, retry will not occur for status codes 400, 401, 403, 410 or 422. This can be overridden here. Note that 2xx codes will never retry as they are considered successful.
        Parameters:
        customRetryForStatusCodes - Mapping of integers (status codes) to booleans (true for retry and false for not retry)
